Demo of Jquery Mobile and HockeyApp.net using PhoneGap

Experimental:

For better control of when an upgrade requester comes and indication in html
Todo: a checkForUpdate with no requester at all.
The isUpdateAvailable is just a variable that is set by other functions if one has called the function first (otherwise the value is "not known" but is false ie not checked).

One can edit BWHockeyManager.m with:

        self.alwaysShowUpdateReminder = NO;
        self.checkForUpdateOnLaunch = NO;
        self.updateSetting = HockeyUpdateCheckManually;

And:

    // do we need to update?
